      "content": "hey, i'm working on this crime thriller script and i need some help with world building. i need a really intense, gritty description of a neighborhood that's basically seen better days. i want the reader to feel the tension and the social decay as soon as they walk onto the block. can u give me some vivid sensory details to make it feel dangerous and unwelcoming?",
